用再忍受这些繁琐的操作，不用回忆应用放在了哪个目录或位置，不用在浪费时间搜索，只需要一个动作，简单地从屏幕边缘滑动手指，就能打开你想要的应用，甚至不用退回到桌面，在其他应用界面也可以触发。</p>\n<h3>一点点小的改变，让自己获得小小的幸福感。</h3>\n<p><em>Google Play</em>: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.panda.swipeon\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.panda.swipeon</a></p>\n<p><img alt=\"intro1\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/Qqqj1sDmHwRW2RD4GaJFbXF7bKUfYjwQX0h3iAYNmrGts4mmIzNlBbSAXL0KSDkiS65f=w1052-h592-rw\"/>\n<img alt=\"intro2\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://play-lh.googleusercontent.com/ANlHGaVEziAns8beO-c1RjhuJY_dQinunIuDKqnm7FRiygh-j5fWSHdmm9OfFVlXah3c=w1052-h592-rw\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1697849144, "replies": 45, "id": 983972}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/45c4/8cce/9_large.png?m=1611468519", "name": "ipad", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/45c4/8cce/9_normal.png?m=1611468519", "title": "iPad", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/ipad", "topics": 1868, "footer": "", "header": "<a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的全新理念的基于 <a href=\"/go/ios\">iOS</a> 的平板电脑。", "title_alternative": "iPad", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/45c4/8cce/9_mini.png?m=1611468519", "stars": 1287, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 9, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"id": 542376, "username": "congfan", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/congfan", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ff62bc7bbbe3a0114f4bb95db7667c1f?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ff62bc7bbbe3a0114f4bb95db7667c1f?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ff62bc7bbbe3a0114f4bb95db7667c1f?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1618309182, "last_modified": 1685726152}, "last_reply